  <div class="info-popup">
    <button class="info-popup-close" data-close="rakeback-popup">&times;</button>
    <h3>Rakeback — 12.5%</h3>
    <p class="info-popup-highlight">You earn back <strong>12.5%</strong> of the house edge on every wager.</p>
